      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 44,
      "message": "But on the other hand in URLValidator.java class constructor, we won't be able to inject all implementations of URLServerViolation interface in a cool way it is now.\nWithout @Service we would have to create object of every implementation. This impact on scalability of code.",
